c: 3
v: 167
t: "And that He might test the hypocrites, it was said to them: \"Come, fight in the Way of Allah or (at least) defend yourselves.\" They said: \"Had we known that fighting will take place, we would certainly have followed you.\" They were that day, nearer to disbelief than to Faith, saying with their mouths what was not in their hearts. And Allah has full knowledge of what they conceal"